   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Appango <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pango, Pago.<text:line-break/>Apparat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Apparo, Paro.<text:line-break/>Appario <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pario. <text:line-break/>Ap parit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Appareo, Pareo.<text:line-break/>Appello, 3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pello.<text:line-break/>Appendicula, -pendix <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Appendeo, Pendeo,<text:line-break/>Appendo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pendo. <text:line-break/>Appetens, Appetent . . ., Appetibilis, Appetisso, Appetit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Appeto, Peto, <text:line-break/>Appingo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pango, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">under</text:span> Pago, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Pingo. <text:line-break/>Applaudo, -plausor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Plaudo.<text:line-break/>Applex, Applic . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Plico.<text:line-break/>Applodo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Plaudo. <text:line-break/>Apploro, Applumbo, Appono <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ploro, Plumbum, Pono.<text:line-break/>Apporrectus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Porrigo, Rego,<text:line-break/>Apport . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Porto.<text:line-break/>Apposco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Posco.<text:line-break/>Apposit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Appono, Pono. <text:line-break/>Appotus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Poto.<text:line-break/>Apprecor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Precor, Preci.<text:line-break/>Apprehendo, -prehensio, -prendo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Prehendo.<text:line-break/>Apprīme <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Primus.<text:line-break/>Apprĭmo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Premo.<text:line-break/>Approb . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Probus.<text:line-break/>Appromitto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Promitto, Mitto.<text:line-break/>Appropero <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Properus. <text:line-break/>Appropinq . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Prope.<text:line-break/>Approprio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Proprius.<text:line-break/>Appugno <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pugno, Pungo. <text:line-break/>Appulsus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Appello, Pello.<text:line-break/>Apra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Aper.<text:line-break/>Apsis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Absis.<text:line-break/>Arabilis, Arat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Aro.</text:p>
