   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">N</text:span>ōnius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. personnamn</text:span> (Non. Marcellus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grammatiker).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Nonnusquam</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: (nusquam, usquam): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Någorstädes:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Noxiōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: (noxia, noceo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skadlig, brottslig:</text:span></text:span> Sen., Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Nŭmĕrōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: (numerus):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Talrikt, på många handa sätt:</text:span></text:span> Col., Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rhythmiskt:</text:span></text:span> dicere; sententia cadit n., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Numnam, Numne, Numquando, Numquid, Numquis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Num.<text:line-break/>Nuncusque <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Nunc. <text:line-break/>Nutus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Nuo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Obbrūtesco</text:span>, tui, 3.: (brutus): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förslöas:</text:span></text:span> animo, Lucr. III. 545.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Obduct . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Obduco, Duco. <text:line-break/>Obduresco, -duro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Durus.<text:line-break/>Object . . ., Objicio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Jacio.<text:line-break/>Obitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Obeo, Eo. Oblaqueo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lacus.<text:line-break/>Oblatr . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lātro. <text:line-break/>Oblido <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lædo.<text:line-break/>Obliteratio, -litero <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Litera.<text:line-break/>Obmutesco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mutus.<text:line-break/>Obnatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Nascor.<text:line-break/>Obnixe <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Obnitor, Nitor. <text:line-break/>Obortus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Oborior, Orior.<text:line-break/>Obrept . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Obrepo, Repo.<text:line-break/>Obretio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Rete. <text:line-break/>Obroboratio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Robur.<text:line-break/>Obscævo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Scævus.<text:line-break/>Obsecund . . ., Obsequ . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sequor.<text:line-break/>Obsitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Obsero, I. Sero. <text:line-break/>Obsŏno <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sonus.<text:line-break/>Obstaculum, -stantia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Obsto, Sto.<text:line-break/>Obstipesco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Stupeo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Obstrāgŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: (sterno): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snörrem:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Obstrictus, Obstrigill . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Obstringo, Stringo.<text:line-break/>Obtemp . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Tempus. <text:line-break/>Obtentus (us) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Obtendo, Tendo.<text:line-break/>Obtest . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Testis.<text:line-break/>Obticentia, -ticeo, -ticesco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Taceo.<text:line-break/>Obtigo = Obtego, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Tego. <text:line-break/>Obtineo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Teneo.<text:line-break/>Obtingo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Tango. <text:line-break/>Obtrect . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Traho.<text:line-break/>Obtritus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Tero. <text:line-break/>Obtunsio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Obtundo, Tundo. <text:line-break/>Occallatus, -callesco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Callum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Occāsiuncŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: (occasio, cado): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Litet tillfälle:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Occedo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cedo.<text:line-break/>Occento <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Canto, Cano.<text:line-break/>Occentus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Occino, Cano. <text:line-break/>Occepto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Occipio, Capio.<text:line-break/>Occidens, -dentalis, Occiduus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Occĭdo, Cado. <text:line-break/>Occīdio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Occīdo, Cædo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Occillo,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slå:</text:span></text:span> os alicui, Pt. Amph. 183.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Occino <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cano.<text:line-break/>Occipio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Capio. <text:line-break/>Occipitium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Caput.<text:line-break/>Occisio, -cisus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Occīdo, Cædo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Occīsor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: (occīdo, cædo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dödare:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Occlamito <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Clamo.<text:line-break/>Occludo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Claudo.<text:line-break/>Occo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Occa.<text:line-break/>Occoepi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Coepi.<text:line-break/>Occubo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cubo.<text:line-break/>Occurro, Occurs . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Curro.<text:line-break/>Octennis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Annus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ŏcŭleus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(oculus): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som består af ögon, är helt och hållet ögon:</text:span> Argus, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">O</text:span>enŏpĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö</text:span> = Aegina. <text:line-break/><text:bookmark text:name="_GoBack"/>Oenŏpĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Offend . . ., Offens . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fendo. <text:line-break/>Offero, -ferumentæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fero.<text:line-break/>Offigo, Offirm . . . Offlecto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Figo, Firmus, Flecto.<text:line-break/>Offoco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fauces.<text:line-break/>Offrenatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frenum. <text:line-break/>Offringo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frango.<text:line-break/>Offucia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Fucus. <text:line-break/>Offula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Offa.<text:line-break/>Offulgeo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fulgeo. <text:line-break/>Offundo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fundo.<text:line-break/>Oggannio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gannio.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Oggero <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gero.<text:line-break/>Oleosus, Oleum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Olea.<text:line-break/>Oleraceus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Olus.<text:line-break/>Omissus, Omitto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mitto.<text:line-break/>Opercul . . ., Operimentum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Operio.<text:line-break/>Operor, Operos . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Opera, III. Opus.<text:line-break/>Opert . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Operio. <text:line-break/>Oppango <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pango, Pago.<text:line-break/>Oppecto, -pexus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pecto.<text:line-break/>Oppedo, Oppessulatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Podo, Pessulus<text:line-break/>Oppico <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pix. <text:line-break/>Oppleo, Opploro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pleo, Ploro.<text:line-break/>Oppono, Opposit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pono.<text:line-break/>Opprobr . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Probrum.<text:line-break/>Oppugn . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pugno, Pungo. <text:line-break/>Opputo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Putus.<text:line-break/>Opta . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Opto.<text:line-break/>Optumus = Optimus.<text:line-break/>Oreæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ōs.<text:line-break/>Osurus, Osus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Odi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Percălĕfăcio</text:span>, fēci, factum, 3.: (caleo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Starkt uppwärma:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Pernĭmius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: (nimis): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blott i neutr.:</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Pernĭmium</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I hög grad för mycket, mycket för mycket:</text:span></text:span> Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Retinnio,</text:span> 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">återklinga:</text:span></text:span> C. (d. l.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕtrŏăgo</text:span>, ēgi, actum, 3.: (ago): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">föra bakåt, tillbaka:</text:span></text:span> Pn., Qu.</text:p>
